<lyrics>[V1]
. C       G         Am       G
 Buǵy qalaı móldir sýdy ańsasa,
.F    G      C
 Meniń janym da
.C    G     Am     G
 Seni izdep shólirkeıdi,
.A     G        C
 Táńir, Seni ańsaıdy.

[C1]
.   Am            F      C
   Qudaıym, Sen qorǵanyshym,
.   F              Dm    G
   Bar úmitim meniń bar kúshim.
.   C     G      Am
   Janymdy da, ómirimdi,
.  F      G     C
   Iem, Ózińe arnadym.</lyrics>
